{"id":162369,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/我爱未未-法兰西24报道：艾未未，艺术家、建筑师/","date":"2011-06-19T03:30:20Z","modified":"2011-06-19T03:30:20Z","title":"我爱未未 | 法兰西24报道：艾未未，艺术家、建筑师和直率的社会批评者","content":"<p><b>艾未未，艺术家、建筑师和直率的社会批评者</b></p>\n<div><b><br /></b></div>\n<div>france24.com 2011年6月18日 法兰西24 链接： <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/bQid9\"> http://goo.gl/bQid9 </a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>内容提要：</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>最新为抗议中国关押艺术家艾未未而取消中国展览的艺术家是雕塑家<span>丹尼尔.布伦</span>Daniel Buren 。法兰西24网站深入报道艾未未，他的政治活动与他的艺术一样将他推向了聚光灯下。</div>\n<div>\n<p><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">刚刚过去的上周</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">，为抗议中国当局羁押</span></span><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">持不同政见的</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">艺术家</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">艾未未，</span></span><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">总部位于伦敦的</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">雕塑家</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">卡普尔</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">拉取消了他</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">在北京</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">中国国家博物馆的一个</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">展览。</span></span></div>\n<div><span><br /><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">现在，</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">法国杰出的</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">雕塑家</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">丹尼尔.布伦也做了同样的事情。</span></span><span>布伦以在</span><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">巴黎</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">的</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">皇宫</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">（靠近</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">卢浮宫）</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">庭院里</span></span><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">黑</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">色相间的条纹柱作品而闻名</span></span><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">，</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">周五他对法国媒体表示，他</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">已取消了</span></span><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">原定</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">七月中旬</span></span><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">在北京</span></span><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">尤伦斯</span></span><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">中国</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">当代艺术</span></span><span>中心</span><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">的</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">展览，以表示艺术家的</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">“团结一致</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">“</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">。</span></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>&#8230;..</span></div>\n<div><span><i><br /></i></span></div>\n<div><i><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">巴黎</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">当代</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">艺术</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">博物馆</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">拉</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">国立</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">美术馆</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">杜</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">Jeu</span> <span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">DE</span> <span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">Paume</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">计划在</span></span><span>2012年初举办</span><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">一个题材丰富的</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">展览，内容是艾未未</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">的摄影</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">和</span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">视频。<a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"more\"></a></span></span></i></div>\n<div><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\"><br /></span></span></div>\n<div><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\">原文链接：</span></span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/bQid9\"> http://goo.gl/bQid9 </a></div>\n<div><span><span title=\"Click for alternate translations\"><br /></span></span></div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/4214948278400391962-1421677793388616813?l=loveaiww.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n<p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/loveAiWeiwei/~4/5AeopqGMLXQ\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":293,"categories":[1],"tags":[9484]}